Titolo: Asphalt 7: Heat

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Asphalt 7: Heat is a 2012 racing video game, developed and published by Gameloft. It is part of the Asphalt series. It was released on June 21, 2012 for the iOS and marks the first time in the series that a game is the same for both the iPhone and iPad. The game was launched for Android on June 25, for BlackBerry 10 on February 21, 2013, for Windows Phone 8 on February 27, for BlackBerry PlayBook on April 3, and for Windows 8 (via Windows Store) on August 22., Windows 10 on July 29, 2015. The game was pulled from the app stores at sometime in 2017.

Genere: Racing 

Valutazione: 83
